{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "拉兹莉 第4话 铁匠之路的交集",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "人类都市\\n拉兹莉的工坊",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110355_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "只要齐心协力，\\n就能发挥超越个人的力量！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120172_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "机械工程师男子",
            "context": "维护匠人的尊严，\\n可比性命更重要啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110355_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "（这世上，除了爷爷之外\\n还有其他优秀的匠人，\\n大家都有自己的路……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110355_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "（我一直走着\\n爷爷教给我的那条路，\\n独自坚持至今……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110355_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "强化、力量吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110355_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "（我应该强化的，\\n一定不只是力量……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110355_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "要是能发现这些不足，\\n现在手里正打造的这把剑，\\n就能变成更好的作品……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110355_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "（要是能找到我自己的路，\\n也许就能在最佳铁匠杯上\\n夺得冠军了！）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "拉兹莉，不好了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110355_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "是你们？怎么了？\\n这么慌张……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110265_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢吉娜",
            "context": "最佳铁匠杯不妙啊！\\n举办遇到危机了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110355_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "诶？诶？什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "大赛主办者正要进行说明呢。\\n你也一起来吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "铁匠1",
            "context": "公会会长！这是怎么回事啊！？\\n竟然说不举办最佳铁匠杯……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "公会会长",
            "context": "这是因为帝国的威胁……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉&罗吉娜",
            "context": "帝国！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "公会会长",
            "context": "最近，各地都发生了帝国绑架\\n机械工程师和铁匠的事件。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110355_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "啊……我被带走的时候，\\n好像听到帝国兵说了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110355_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "在那座废弃矿山以外的地方，\\n还在让铁匠打造武器。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "那么，帝国下一个目标就是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "公会会长",
            "context": "没错……应该就是\\n参加最佳铁匠杯的优秀铁匠们。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "公会会长",
            "context": "大赛的举办地、时间都已经公布……\\n帝国很有可能趁机来捣乱。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "公会会长",
            "context": "我作为主办者，\\n有责任保护参赛者的安全。\\n因此本次大赛决定中止。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "铁匠1",
            "context": "可恶！我就是为了这一天\\n才一路磨炼技艺至今……\\n就因为这种事……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "铁匠2",
            "context": "是啊，该死的帝国！\\n竟然搅黄我们铁匠\\n赌上尊严的重要大赛！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110355_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "不能中止……\\n因为我们可是匠人啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "拉兹莉？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110355_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "没法很好地表达我想说的……\\n因为我也还在摸索。但是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110355_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "匠人们走着各自不同的道路，\\n每个人重视的东西也不一样……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110355_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "但是，大家的目标\\n一定都是一样的，\\n都想成为顶级匠人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110355_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "在场的铁匠们所走的道路\\n都通往最佳铁匠杯……\\n没错吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "嗯……说得对。\\n绝对不能让出这条路。\\n就算拼上性命也想守护它！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "铁匠1",
            "context": "没错！为了在大赛中夺冠，\\n我已经赌上了一切！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "铁匠2",
            "context": "是啊！大陆第一铁匠的称号\\n可是大家的梦想！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110355_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "拜托了，公会会长！\\n如期举办最佳铁匠杯吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "公会会长",
            "context": "可是……万一被帝国抓住，\\n梦想和尊严可就都……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110355_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "没事的。我……不，我们会\\n拼命战斗守护这一切！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110355_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "大家……愿意助我一臂之力吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "铁匠1",
            "context": "当然！我要证明\\n只要拥有我打造的武器，\\n就天下无敌！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "铁匠2",
            "context": "是啊！\\n怕帝国还当什么铁匠啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "公会会长",
            "context": "你们真的确定？比起性命，\\n更愿意选择身为匠人的志向……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "公会会长",
            "context": "好吧！既然说到这个份上，\\n大赛就如期举行吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "公会会长",
            "context": "只是！有一个条件——\\n变更大赛的举办地！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110265_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢吉娜",
            "context": "诶？什、什么意思……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110355_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "就是说要在\\n没有帝国兵的地方举办吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "公会会长",
            "context": "呵呵……没有那么消极，\\n是个更好的主意。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "公会会长",
            "context": "我们要让帝国领教一下……\\n践踏铁匠的志向是什么下场！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}